{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Condemn the plans to ban hijab in France",
        "additional_details": "We believe Islamophobia is deepening in France, and this plan is cruel and unfair.\r\n \r\nOur Government should publicly condemn this.\r\n \r\nThis cruel action will mean many Muslim women in France feel unable to leave their homes. It will alienate Muslim residents in France further than they already are.\r\n \r\nThis action may mean many Muslim people leave France, if they can.\r\n \r\nAs an ally to France, our Government should let them know that this plan is unacceptable.",
        "background": "The Senate in France has voted:\r\n \r\n\u2014No girl under the age of 18 can wear a hijab in public.\r\n\u2014Mothers with hijab cannot accompany their kids on school trips.",
